		<section id="definition_list_term">
			<p>A definition list is a structure for listing terms, products, components, and so forth, along with their definitions.</p>
			<p>
				Examples of usage are glossary and product feature lists.</p>
			<p>
				<b>Example</b>
			</p>
			<p>
				<codeblock>
&lt;section id="knownproblems_info"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can get current information about bugs, 
patches, and change requests in the following locations:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;dl&gt;
&lt;dlentry&gt;
&lt;dt&gt;Bug tracker&lt;/dt&gt;
&lt;dd&gt;
